          <title>Mayor Eric Adams federal bribery case dismissed</title>
          <description><![CDATA[NEW YORK CITY (PIX11) -- Mayor Eric Adams' federal bribery case has been dismissed, court records show. In a letter filed Wednesday, Judge Dale Ho ordered the case dropped with prejudice, meaning the government cannot bring these charges against Adams again in the future.]]></description>
